# Runtime Model

This starter document should be completed from the current generated artifacts during finalization.

## Default Loop Runtime

- Mail-driven loops are notifier-prompt-driven.
- A separate Houmao notifier process detects open mail and prompts the target agent.
- After processing mail and any requested follow-up tick, the agent ends the chat turn.
- Do not rely on in-chat waiting, sleeping, polling, or periodic background tick workers.

